e called \"20% Chance of Flurries,\" in Casper, Wyoming. The work, by artist Chris Navarro, is a tongue-in-cheek reference to Wyoming cowboys' lot in winter: unpredictable, sideways blizzards in which they have to work, saving livestock, sometimes including newborn calves and lambs who would starve and freeze to death in the bitter cold", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2017688157/"}], "resource": {"fulltext_file": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/wyu/batch_wyu_frannie_ver01/data/sn86072160/00514150369/1921012501/0180.xml&format=alto_xml&full_text=1", "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:wyu:batch_wyu_frannie_ver01:data:sn86072160:00514150369:1921012501:0179/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg", "pdf": "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/ndnp/wyu/batch_wyu_frannie_ver01/data/sn86072160/00514150369/1921012501/0180.pdf", "segment_count": 8, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn86072160/1921-01-25/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}, "resources": [{"fulltext_file": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/wyu/batch_wyu_frannie_ver01/data/sn86072160/00514150369/1921012501/0180.xml&format=alto_xml&full_text=1", "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:wyu:batch_wyu_frannie_ver01:data:sn86072160:00514150369:1921012501:0179/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg", "pdf": "https://tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/ndnp/wyu/batch_wyu_frannie_ver01/data/sn86072160/00514150369/1921012501/0180.pdf", "segment_count": 8, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn86072160/1921-01-25/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}], "segment_id": "/service/ndnp/wyu/batch_wyu_frannie_ver01/data/sn86072160/00514150369/1921012501/0180.xml", "segments": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn86072160/1921-01-25/ed-1/?sp=2"],